body.name: Brother HL-L6310DW Enterprise Monochrome Laser Printer with Low-Cost Printing, Wireless Networking, and Large Paper Capacity
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Tuesday, February 13. Order within 4 hrs 53 mins
features: FAST PRINTING FOR INCREASED EFFICIENCY: The Brother HL-L6310DW enterprise monochrome laser printer delivers high-quality output and a print speed of up to 52ppm(1) to help boost productivity and ensure fast, professional quality documents for mid to large-sized workgroups.

LIFETIME VALUE: Offers built-in value with an included Brother Genuine 6,000-page toner cartridge. For even lower cost printing, use the Brother Genuine TN920UXXL ultra high-yield replacement toner cartridge for 18,000 pages(2).

ENTERPRISE LEVEL SECURITY FEATURES: Equipped with Triple Layer Security features to help safeguard your network, keep your devices secure, and protect documents in transit to and from print devices. Includes an integrated NFC card reader for easy badge authentication.

LARGE, EXPANDABLE PAPER CAPACITY: Spend less time refilling paper trays with the 520-sheet capacity paper tray, 100-sheet capacity multipurpose tray for printing on custom media or envelopes, and 250-sheet output capacity(3). Total capacity is expandable up to 1,660 sheets with optional trays(4). An optional cabinet can be used to store paper and supplies and turn the printer into a floor-standing configuration(4).

EASY TO USE, DEPLOY, AND MANAGE: Equipped with device management solutions to enable mass distribution of device configurations, security settings, firmware updates, and task automation. User friendly design allows for easy replacement of paper and toner.
body.description: The Brother HL-L6310DW enterprise monochrome laser printer offers enterprise-level performance, advanced security features, and reliable, high-quality output for mid to large-sized workgroups. This high-performance printer helps to increase productivity with a fast print speed of up to 52ppm(1). Offers built-in value with an included Brother Genuine 6,000-page toner cartridge. For even lower cost printing, use the Brother Genuine TN920UXXL ultra high-yield replacement toner cartridge for 18,000 pages(2). Triple Layer Security features help to limit document and device access and protect against network intrusions. Includes an integrated NFC card reader for easy badge authentication. Spend less time refilling paper trays with the 520-sheet capacity paper tray, 100-sheet capacity multipurpose tray for printing on custom media or envelopes, and 250-sheet output capacity(3). Total capacity is expandable up to 1,660 sheets with optional trays(4). An optional cabinet can be used to store paper and supplies and turn the printer into a floor-standing configuration(4). Equipped with device management solutions to enable mass distribution of device configurations, security settings, firmware updates, and task automation. User friendly design allows for easy replacement of paper and toner. Features built-in Gigabit Ethernet and dual band wireless networking to seamlessly set up and share on your wired or wireless network. Easily print from a wide variety of mobile devices(5). Color touchscreen display offers easy menu navigation and the ability to print directly from popular business cloud services(6). ENERGY STAR® certified and EPEAT® Silver rated. Help save paper with default duplex printing. Eco Mode helps to reduce power consumption, while Toner Save Mode helps to reduce toner use. One-year limited warranty with free online, live chat, or phone support for the life of your product. 1 Based on one-sided printing. Change from default setting required. 2 Approximate toner cartridge yield in accordance with ISO/IEC 19752 (letter/A4). 3 Maximum capacity based on using 20 lb. paper. 4 Requires additional purchase. 5 Additional download required. Compatibility may vary by device or operating system. Wireless connection may be required. 6 Requires an Internet connection and an account with desired service.
